There are distinct differences in the immune response to infection in the natural reservoir versus spillover to humans. In the natural reservoir for HTV, there is little to no pro-inflammatory response during the early stages in the lung; but in later stages of the infection, anti-inflammatory cytokine levels and tumour growth factor (TGF-\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
